<span class='au'>Dominguez, C. X., Amezquita, R. A., Guan, T. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">The transcription factors ZEB2 and T-bet cooperate to program cytotoxic T cell terminal differentiation in response to LCMV viral infection.</span> <span class='so'>J. Exp. Med., 212, 2041-2056 (2015)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26503446" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R14"><span class='au'>Liu, C. F., Brandt, G. S., Hoang, Q. Q. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Crystal structure of the DNA binding domain of the transcription factor T-bet suggests simultaneous recognition of distant genome sites.</span> <span class='so'>Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. USA, 113, E6572-E6581 (2016)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/27791029" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R15"><span class='au'>Sekimata, M., PErez-Melgosa, M., Miller, S. A. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">CCCTC-binding factor and the transcription factor T-bet orchestrate T helper 1 cell-specific structure and function at the interferon-γ locus.</span> <span class='so'>Immunity, 31, 551-564 (2009)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/19818655" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br></ol><br><h2>活用したデータベースにかかわるキーワードと統合TVへのリンク</h2><br><ul><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=GEO" target="_blank">GEO</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=UCSC" target="_blank">UCSC</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=Ensembl" target="_blank">Ensembl</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=KEGG" target="_blank">KEGG</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=塩基配列" target="_blank">塩基配列解析</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=アラインメント" target="_blank">アラインメント</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=パスウェイ解析" target="_blank">パスウェイ解析</a></li><br><li><a href="http://togotv.dbcls.jp/ja/tags.html?tag=RNA-seq" target="_b